
# Dataset Description

## Project Title

**Strategic Product Placement Analysis Using Tableau**

---

# 1. Introduction

This dataset has been created for the SmartBridge Virtual Internship project titled **"Strategic Product Placement Analysis Using Tableau."**

The dataset represents retail sales transactions from different store types, regions, and product categories. It is designed to analyze the effect of product placement, pricing, discounts, and customer demographics on sales performance using Tableau dashboards.

The dataset enables Business Intelligence analysis through interactive visualizations and supports data-driven decision-making for retail businesses.

